{"tid":2498398,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【定息按揭】推出接近一年得50宗申請 6成人揀定息10年","createTime":"2021-04-21T06:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T07:49:21.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7953fa6149c5051462deed9aad48bbabb299f865","tid":2498398,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:34:35.000Z","msg":"【定息按揭】推出接近一年得50宗申請 6成人揀定息10年<br />\n12:07 2021/04/21<br />\n<br />\n&quot;政府去年推出長年期的定息按貸款，至今接近一年時間，不過市場反應冷淡，截至今年3月底只有50宗申請，其中36宗已經批出，涉及約1.9億元，只及政府預留貸款規模的2成，當局指試申請期仍然有半年時會，會檢討計劃成效再決定下一步的安排......<br />\n<br />\n......數據顯示，以10年期定息的計劃相對較受歡迎，涉及30宗，佔整體比例6成，其中19宗已經批出，平均貸款額為525萬元......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2937408/%E3%80%90%E5%AE%9A%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%89%E6%8F%AD%E3%80%91%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%9750%E5%AE%97%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%20%206%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%80%E5%AE%9A%E6%81%AF10%E5%B9%B4?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2937408%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%258C%2589%25E6%258F%25AD%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E8%25BF%2591%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BE%259750%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%2520%25206%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2581%25AF10%25E5%25B9%25B4%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dB5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=aa6a6121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2937408/%E3%80%90%E5%AE%9A%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%89%E6%8F%AD%E3%80%91%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%9750%E5%AE%97%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%20%206%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%80%E5%AE%9A%E6%81%AF10%E5%B9%B4?mtc=60037</a>"},{"pid":"66e836676ff384ea93ba3a5fe00bb4f21f1f3fed","tid":2498398,"uid":345941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:46:47.000Z","msg":"息又高，年期又短，除非過唔到壓測先唔做<br />\n<br />\n銀行啲staff又唔識，就算你想做佢哋都耍走你"},{"pid":"7837009fb